{"tid":2262633,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"【狂賀】何妖被皇仁舊生會發信DQ會籍","createTime":"2020-10-29T09:02:21.000Z","updateTime":"2020-10-30T03:19:37.000Z","uid":321059,"like":47,"dislike":1,"uniUserReply":12,"replies":[{"pid":"543c5faad9cd3b6ced84f8b29b9350f62129b1ae","tid":2262633,"uid":321059,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-10-29T09:02:21.000Z","msg":"<a href=\"https://hk.nextmgz.com/webarticle/2_764564_0\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fhk.nextmgz.com%2Fwebarticle%2F2_764564_0&d=2u41qa%2Bce9Gslgrzp%2F5KireFZk%2BLn%2Bp4m9s6a9hK%2BPA%3D&h=38b56a1c\" data-ef-url=\"https://embed.lih.kg/frame?u=https%3A%2F%2Fhk.nextmgz.com%2Fwebarticle%2F2_764564_0&h=6acb92df\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://hk.nextmgz.com/webarticle/2_764564_0</a><br />\n<br />\n問卷於去年9月已經完成，共有781位會員回應，而針對何君堯被DQ的一題中，<span class=\"x-large\"><span class=\"gold\">有83.2%的人表示應要通過DQ何君堯。</span></span><br />\n<br />\n有不願出名的皇仁舊生表示，很多舊生正在歡呼，認為舊生會此時公佈消息，實在令他們呼一口悶氣。<br />\n<br />\n<span class=\"x-large\"><span class=\"orange\">皇仁仔好波</span></span><br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/wine_connect.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/wine_connect.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/wine_connect.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"dcd0a81cfc19e46112e981349f16377ecfc32286","tid":2262633,"uid":2419,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-10-29T09:03:16.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"657afdabd854476332569307d3d54571dc519eca","tid":2262633,"uid":356542,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-10-29T09:05:00.000Z","msg":"此回覆已被刪除"},{"pid":"33f872797b138b37d94dbe39b9abf78fc798008b","tid":2262633,"uid":53026,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"reply